The paper deals with the task of learning local descriptors for computer vision applications, which is a common topic in the computer vision community. The proposed method involves regularization and optimization techniques, which are commonly used in machine learning and optimization research. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). However, the paper also involves deep learning techniques, which are commonly used in the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves evaluation on image and video datasets, which are commonly used in the sub-categories of cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
